summary: I just joined the andi mack fandom, and I have no clue how to get followers and stuff on tumblr haha. Any tips?
question: I just joined the andi mack fandom, and I have no clue how to get followers and stuff on tumblr haha. Any tips?
answer:
Original posts! Reblogging and liking is great but making your own content is what will get you to show up on someone else’s dash. Try to put thought and quality into those things! Even if they’re funny/crackt still make sure you enjoy what you’re posting, it’ll make it more enjoyable for everyone. 

Also make sure you tag your posts with tags RELEVANT to what you’re posting (don’t tag something as muffy if it isn’t about muffy) there’s nothing worse than seeing a blogger who tags a million popular things just to get their post noticed. 

Also adding funny or interesting ideas to other people’s posts is a good way to meet people. If you have similar ideas or opinions as people they’ll tend to enjoy all your content, that’s how i end up following most blogs I do.

Don’t be afraid to post or get involved in things. The friendom is constantly doing/hosting open collabs/holiday things/games/polls/etc. It’s lowkey one of the most interactive fandoms ive ever been in.
